data.description: Martin's Mill ISD - Versatility is key here! Live a simple life off the land or run a full-out business - the choice is yours w]the limitless opportunities. Main home features approx. 3000sf of beautiful wood finishes. Downstairs master w]add. bedroom or office & add. full guest bathroom, separate laundry, walk-in fire rated safe - upstairs you'll find 3bdrms, 1ba & an open game rm. The main living area of the home is perfect for a crowd, also offers a huge separate family room. Guest house provides 2 add. bdrms & full bath with washer]dryer, kitchen and combo living]dining area. Water well w]filtration, stocked ponds, woods, pastures, pens 40x40 equip barn & 30x40 workshop. Ag exempt - some cows can remain.
